import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-edit-listing', templateUrl: './edit-listing.component.html', styleUrls: ['./edit-listing.component.css'] }) export class EditListingComponent { public listingToEdit: CarListing = { year: '', make: '', model: '' }; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + `api/carlisting/find`).subscribe(result => { this.listingToEdit = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface CarListing { year: string; make: string; model: string; driveAwayPrice?: number; excludingGovernmentCharges?: number; nonDealerDetails?: { name: string; contactNumber: string; } dealerDetails?: { name: string; email: string; contactNumber: string; abn: string; } }
